# EILLON Brand Voice

Read `DESIGN.md` for full rules.

## Voice
Quiet · sensory · precise · architectural · intimate · slow · confident · commercially clear, never loud.

## Good
- "Prickly pear, held against mineral air."
- "Receive the Beles restock note before the public boutique opens."
- "The Letter is sent slowly: studio notes, restock windows, and private appointment openings."

## Forbidden patterns
Everyone is obsessed · smell irresistible · main character energy · luxury vibes · dupe · compliment getter · guaranteed long-lasting · seductive · exotic · oriental · ancient secret · fake scarcity

## Claims
Never invent stock, restock dates, awards, press quotes, or testimonials. Align product notes with `data/products.js` and `beles.html`.

## Culture
Afro-Mediterranean memory — precise, never flattening or exoticizing.
